p: For all influenza viruses combined, the models did not identify any significant correlates (Figure 2M‐P). The estimated OR was 0.90 [0.76, 1.07] ( P = .24) for precipitation, 0.89 [0.73, 1.08] ( P = .26) for RH, 0.90 [0.75, 1.07] ( P = .23) for AH, and 0.85 [0.70, 1.04] ( P > .05 for all 3 models) for temperature.
